{"tid":511103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦指林鄭述職期間　倡香港於大灣區辦學、辦醫院、養老中心","createTime":"2017-12-27T06:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T07:02:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"50eac7a273bbc0ea574ef6f26710496c7b0f7664","tid":511103,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥本月中上京述職後，曾向傳媒透露已就粵港澳大灣區發展，向中央政府爭取做到人流、物流、資金流、信息流全面流通。國務院港澳辦昨在網頁公佈，林鄭述職期間曾與澳門特首崔世安提出，希望中央政府支援港澳在大灣區開辦醫院、學校、健康養老中心等具體專案。<br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳辦網頁昨公布，港澳辦上周四召開黨組（擴大）會議，傳達學習貫徹早前中央經濟工作會議精神，港澳辦主任張曉明提到，香港特首林鄭月娥及澳門特首崔世安早前上京述職時，提出希望中央政府支持港澳在大灣區開辦醫院、學校、健康養老中心等具體項目，港澳辦會結合港珠澳大橋通車配套相關的政策措施，進行政策、制度和管理創新，務實推進合作。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明又說，港澳辦同時要結合港澳特首不久前來京述職時，提出希望中央支援港澳在大灣區開辦醫院、學校、健康養老中心等具體項目，並結合與港珠澳大橋通車配套相關的政策措施，進行政策、制度和管理創新，務實推進合作。會議又要求各級領導幹部進一步加強學習和實踐，多做調查研究，切實提高開展港澳工作的能力和水平，奮力開創「一國兩制」事業新局面。<br />\n<br />\n不過，而林鄭月娥本月中述職後，被問及曾向中央提出了甚麼要求時，她只表示爭取中央支持在大灣區做到人流、物流、資金流、信息流全面流通，令大灣區經濟體可以成熟發展，未有提及上述具體建議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%BF%B0%E8%81%B7%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93-%E5%80%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%96%BC%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%BE%A6%E5%AD%B8-%E8%BE%A6%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E9%A4%8A%E8%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%2593-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%25A4%258A%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&d=NVi04CGZMQiyBxT8TxLyVjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=fdd53201\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%2593-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%25A4%258A%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&h=0670a0ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%BF%B0%E8%81%B7%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93-%E5%80%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%96%BC%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%BE%A6%E5%AD%B8-%E8%BE%A6%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E9%A4%8A%E8%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</a>"},{"pid":"db0de293836d2ec6557918c0b23549fb4fcad1ab","tid":511103,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"搞養老中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好起返十間八間<br />\n醫療同護理技術標準跟返中国標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛國丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3a2fec5ad0369537f8ef0b062e036bb9e7e583","tid":511103,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"送哂班死廢老返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7ddc7ed6586c9c97a420c7d226ba2e9f188b0c","tid":511103,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0de293836d2ec6557918c0b23549fb4fcad1ab","tid":511103,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"搞養老中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa